Dialogue: 1,0:00:02.23,0:00:06.61,title,,0,0,0,,{\an1\blur0.5}Summer Time Rendering
Dialogue: 5,0:00:02.56,0:00:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I actually thought I was dead, Shinpei.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:10.24,0:00:12.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Shide...
Dialogue: 5,0:00:16.27,0:00:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Haine...
Dialogue: 5,0:00:17.77,0:00:20.67,Default,,0,0,0,,No, Hiruko.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:21.07,0:00:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yer worthless trash now.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:24.65,0:00:27.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You've shrunken so much.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:27.37,0:00:30.04,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way you'll recover.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:30.59,0:00:33.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Yer eyes are broken now.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:33.29,0:00:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just so disappointed in ya.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:36.56,0:00:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,But look at yer right eye!
Dialogue: 5,0:00:39.52,0:00:41.71,Default,,0,0,0,,That is the observer's right eye.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:41.71,0:00:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Ya must be the egg.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:43.54,0:00:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You've just awakened!
Dialogue: 5,0:00:47.53,0:00:49.74,Default,,0,0,0,,But why?
Dialogue: 5,0:00:49.74,0:00:55.41,Default,,0,0,0,,When Haine looked, most of yer data was corrupt.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:55.41,0:01:01.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't realize that'd become what ya developed into.
Dialogue: 5,0:01:01.12,0:01:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess only someone like ya were able to be restored.
Dialogue: 5,0:01:06.59,0:01:09.47,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's the power of love!
Dialogue: 5,0:01:09.47,0:01:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,If I can take yer eye from ya, my dreams will still come true.
Dialogue: 5,0:01:15.00,0:01:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I failed to take it from Shinpei who had it in the fourth loop,
Dialogue: 5,0:01:21.84,0:01:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}but I can take it from the egg who still has it.
Dialogue: 5,0:01:26.52,0:01:30.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If what he really wants is what I \Nsaw in his mind at that moment...
Dialogue: 5,0:01:33.77,0:01:35.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not letting him get it!
Dialogue: 5,0:01:35.81,0:01:39.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Shide... wait...
Dialogue: 5,0:01:39.72,0:01:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I can still do it...
Dialogue: 5,0:01:43.10,0:01:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,If I eat enough humans, I'll get better.
Dialogue: 5,0:01:48.42,0:01:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,So come home with me.
Dialogue: 5,0:01:52.84,0:01:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,M-Maybe take Ushio's eye... and give it to m-me.
Dialogue: 5,0:01:58.80,0:02:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't need ya anymore.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:01.34,0:02:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 5,0:02:02.70,0:02:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Ain't Haine yer mother?
Dialogue: 5,0:02:05.20,0:02:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,So?
Dialogue: 5,0:02:06.91,0:02:09.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care about the past.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:10.77,0:02:14.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Shide!
Dialogue: 5,0:02:15.24,0:02:18.91,Default,,0,0,0,,And ya call yerself human!
Dialogue: 5,0:02:18.91,0:02:22.25,Default,,0,0,0,,However, I need Hiruko to stay alive.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:22.25,0:02:26.21,Default,,0,0,0,,If she dies, my armor will disappear.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:26.60,0:02:31.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take ya home, as ya wish!
Dialogue: 5,0:02:32.08,0:02:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No, I'm not going like this...
Dialogue: 5,0:02:40.68,0:02:43.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Come, Observer.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:44.12,0:02:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's settle the matter over there.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:50.55,0:02:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Ushio!
Dialogue: 5,0:02:51.75,0:02:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Gimme Nezu's weapon!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:06.73,0:03:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Shide!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:15.23,0:03:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinpei!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:26.95,0:03:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:29.47,0:03:30.31,Default,,0,0,0,,This is bad!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:30.31,0:03:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinpei, we're being drawn in!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:33.57,0:03:35.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm weak.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:35.09,0:03:35.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Too weak!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:36.62,0:03:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Mortals can't go past this point!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:38.33,0:03:41.61,Default,,0,0,0,,If ya do, ya can't leave nor die!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:41.61,0:03:43.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll end up lost!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:44.25,0:03:45.37,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 5,0:03:45.65,0:03:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go by myself!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:47.08,0:03:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:48.25,0:03:50.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm never leaving ya again!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:50.29,0:03:54.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Dummy! Were ya listening to me? Yer so stubborn!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:54.39,0:03:57.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryuu, can ya hear me? Take Shinpei and go!
Dialogue: 5,0:04:00.19,0:04:04.35,Default,,0,0,0,,If I leave ya now, Sis will never forgive me.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:04.94,0:04:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryuu!
Dialogue: 5,0:04:06.36,0:04:09.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Sis made a promise with ya.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:09.91,0:04:11.77,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm gonna keep it fer her.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:11.77,0:04:14.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be Shinpei's support.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:14.47,0:04:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't let him get lost!
Dialogue: 5,0:04:19.77,0:04:22.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll follow yer presence.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:23.08,0:04:23.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Always!
Dialogue: 5,0:04:25.49,0:04:27.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be by yer side.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:27.92,0:04:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I love ya, and I wanna be with ya.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:32.12,0:04:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Got a problem with that?
Dialogue: 5,0:04:40.09,0:04:41.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Dummy.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:44.35,0:04:47.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinpei!
Dialogue: 5,0:04:53.34,0:04:54.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Sou!
Dialogue: 5,0:04:54.85,0:04:56.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Take care of everyone!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:22.91,0:05:23.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Ushio!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:40.60,0:05:43.78,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Haine's home.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:45.99,0:05:45.99,Default,chapter,0,0,0,,{Part A}
Dialogue: 5,0:05:52.12,0:05:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Where's Ushio?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.63,0:06:02.17,ep title,,0,1533,0,,{\bord7\c&HD1AD37&\alpha&H30&\blur7\3c&HD1AD37&}Endless Night
Dialogue: 1,0:05:58.63,0:06:02.17,ep title,,0,1533,0,,{\blur0.5}Endless Night
Dialogue: 5,0:06:03.51,0:06:06.35,Default,,0,0,0,,The flow of time is cut off here.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:06.93,0:06:09.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just like how Dr. Hishigata said.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:09.22,0:06:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 5,0:06:10.10,0:06:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Time doesn't flow here.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:12.30,0:06:14.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It's stagnant.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:14.69,0:06:17.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I don't think I can go back by looping.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:17.25,0:06:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If I die, that's probably it.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:20.57,0:06:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't good.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:26.09,0:06:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Ushio!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:36.01,0:06:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I just had her in my hand!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:40.87,0:06:42.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I know she's here.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:43.74,0:06:47.09,Default,,0,0,0,,The shotgun that she printed hasn't disappeared.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:47.41,0:06:49.64,Default,,0,0,0,,So she's within 50 meters.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:50.17,0:06:52.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I can sense her faintly too.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:52.17,0:06:54.14,Default,,0,0,0,,She's on the move.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:54.14,0:06:55.90,Default,,0,0,0,,L-Let's go after her!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:57.32,0:06:59.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinpei! I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:59.47,0:07:00.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because I jumped.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:00.70,0:07:06.13,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I told you to go after Shide with everything you had.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:06.13,0:07:09.71,Default,,0,0,0,,This is nothing compared to what Ms. Nagumo went through.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:11.92,0:07:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me control your body.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:14.72,0:07:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take on the pain.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:17.24,0:07:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,But then you'll be hurting.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:19.38,0:07:20.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be okay.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:20.69,0:07:22.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a shadow.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:22.34,0:07:24.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I can tune down the sense of pain.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:25.13,0:07:27.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not just your leg injury.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:29.01,0:07:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Your entire body is starting to give out.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:32.10,0:07:38.17,Default,,0,0,0,,If I don't support ya internally, ya won't have a chance here.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:46.41,0:07:47.44,Default,,0,0,0,,How does it feel?
Dialogue: 5,0:07:47.44,0:07:49.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to move your body now.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:49.49,0:07:51.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It feels strange.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:51.36,0:07:55.45,Default,,0,0,0,,My body is numb, yet I'm conscious.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:55.85,0:08:01.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It's usually like that for me too, \Nbut being conscious only is weird.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:01.53,0:08:06.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, but it's kind of like when I take a bird's-eve view. I can get used to it.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:10.38,0:08:12.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Ushio!
Dialogue: 5,0:08:13.87,0:08:15.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Can ya hear me?
Dialogue: 5,0:08:16.77,0:08:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Ushio!
Dialogue: 5,0:08:22.36,0:08:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ryuunosuke, is this Hitogashima?
Dialogue: 5,0:08:27.30,0:08:28.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks similar.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:28.74,0:08:31.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I can see the Wakayama mainland across the sea.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:31.92,0:08:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:35.77,0:08:37.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Shinpei?
Dialogue: 5,0:08:37.74,0:08:40.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I meant to tell ya this earlier.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:40.27,0:08:41.33,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 5,0:08:41.83,0:08:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Ya don't have to speak so formally to me.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:45.25,0:08:48.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yer older than I am.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:48.09,0:08:51.22,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you're the same age as Ms. Nagumo,
Dialogue: 5,0:08:51.22,0:08:52.34,Default,,0,0,0,,so you're much older!
Dialogue: 5,0:08:52.34,0:08:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'm in junior high. When I died, that is.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:56.23,0:08:59.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Ushio immediately called me Ryuu.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:59.29,0:09:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, she's extremely friendly to anyone.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:03.01,0:09:08.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not the type who's super casual just because you're younger.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:09.10,0:09:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Are ya always so formal with anyone?
Dialogue: 5,0:09:11.21,0:09:12.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:12.43,0:09:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm more casual with people my age.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:16.47,0:09:18.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? So what about Mio?
Dialogue: 5,0:09:18.95,0:09:20.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Yer super casual with her.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:20.54,0:09:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,That took getting used to.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:25.71,0:09:27.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a bit jealous.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:30.76,0:09:33.18,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case, I'm gonna go casual with ya!
Dialogue: 5,0:09:33.18,0:09:33.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 5,0:09:33.77,0:09:36.14,Default,,0,0,0,,So be totally casual with me too! Ya got it?!
Dialogue: 5,0:09:36.41,0:09:38.43,Default,,0,0,0,,The way I speak is how I show respect.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:38.43,0:09:41.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't mean we're not close.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:41.29,0:09:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,No, our lingo is super important!
Dialogue: 5,0:09:43.86,0:09:48.07,Default,,0,0,0,,So please... uh... just do it!
Dialogue: 5,0:09:50.53,0:09:52.99,Default,,0,0,0,,What's so funny?
Dialogue: 5,0:09:53.83,0:09:59.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It makes me want to get to know you more, Ryuunosuke.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:01.81,0:10:02.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:04.11,0:10:04.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:06.42,0:10:07.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Look.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:15.93,0:10:17.01,Default,,0,0,0,,A ball?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:20.86,0:10:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I've seen it before.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:23.55,0:10:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's Haine's ball.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:26.44,0:10:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go after it.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:27.63,0:10:28.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger that.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:47.23,0:10:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ryuunosuke, see that sign?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:50.86,0:10:52.83,Default,,0,0,0,,"Tekram"...
Dialogue: 5,0:10:52.83,0:10:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,No, Kobayakawa Market?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:56.47,0:10:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Wha—
Dialogue: 5,0:10:59.57,0:11:00.89,Default,,0,0,0,,What are these things?
Dialogue: 5,0:11:08.91,0:11:10.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Are they shadows?
Dialogue: 5,0:11:10.77,0:11:15.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Dunno, but they don't seem like they'll attack us.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:25.46,0:11:26.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Ushio!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:31.80,0:11:34.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Ushio, are ya okay?!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:34.21,0:11:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me what happened!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:36.53,0:11:37.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinpei...
Dialogue: 5,0:11:39.13,0:11:40.89,Default,,0,0,0,,My head...
Dialogue: 5,0:11:45.04,0:11:48.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-This presence...
Dialogue: 5,0:11:49.34,0:11:50.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Haine!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:54.13,0:11:55.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I promised Ushio.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:56.80,0:11:59.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Her body is a part of Haine's.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:00.49,0:12:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,If Ushio loses herself and Haine appears, I'll kill her.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:08.78,0:12:12.67,Default,,0,0,0,,If I'm no longer around, Ryuunosuke...
Dialogue: 5,0:12:15.42,0:12:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You need to keep that promise.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:21.60,0:12:24.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinpei, I'm gonna shoot! I will!
Dialogue: 5,0:12:25.09,0:12:26.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay?!
Dialogue: 5,0:12:28.09,0:12:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinpei?
Dialogue: 5,0:12:29.88,0:12:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold it, Ryuunosuke.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:32.17,0:12:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,She's saying something.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:33.68,0:12:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:35.92,0:12:38.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine now, Ryuu.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:39.34,0:12:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,She's different.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:41.28,0:12:44.43,Default,,0,0,0,,She's not the evil Haine who killed ya.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:45.75,0:12:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Her consciousness split at that moment into the human girl Haine and Hiruko.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:55.00,0:12:57.72,Default,,0,0,0,,So who's inside ya, Ushio?
Dialogue: 5,0:12:58.36,0:13:00.43,Default,,0,0,0,,A girl who loves sweets.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:00.97,0:13:02.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Ms. Nagumo's friend.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:03.92,0:13:05.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Her friend?
Dialogue: 5,0:13:05.35,0:13:06.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:07.20,0:13:08.81,Default,,0,0,0,,And she's also...
Dialogue: 5,0:13:09.97,0:13:11.02,Default,,0,0,0,,me.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:12.08,0:13:14.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Haine wants to talk to ya.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:14.05,0:13:15.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Will ya listen to her?
Dialogue: 5,0:13:17.68,0:13:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:22.68,0:13:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:34.43,0:13:36.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet ya.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:37.00,0:13:37.00,Default,chapter,0,0,0,,{Part B}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.00,0:13:40.22,title,,0,0,0,,{\an1\bord5\c&HC0A038&\blur7}Summer Time Rendering
Dialogue: 1,0:13:37.00,0:13:40.22,title,,0,0,0,,{\an1\blur0.5}Summer Time Rendering
Dialogue: 5,0:13:40.12,0:13:41.34,Default,,0,0,0,,So yer...
Dialogue: 5,0:13:44.97,0:13:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Ya don't gotta be shy.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:46.63,0:13:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,,They're Hizuru's friends.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:49.11,0:13:50.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:51.89,0:13:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I had a long dream.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:54.50,0:13:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It was Ushio's memory.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:57.13,0:14:00.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Shinpei, Ryuunosuke.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:00.27,0:14:02.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I got everyone involved...
Dialogue: 5,0:14:02.91,0:14:06.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You, Hizuru, and Ushio...
Dialogue: 5,0:14:06.41,0:14:08.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone died because of me.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:09.11,0:14:11.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not yer place to apologize.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:11.95,0:14:14.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Hiruko was the one who ate me.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:14.13,0:14:16.29,Default,,0,0,0,,That's just what she does.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:17.00,0:14:19.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Shide is to blame, fer taking advantage of that.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:22.39,0:14:25.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yer going to fight Shide?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:32.94,0:14:34.81,Default,,0,0,0,,We're in an endless night.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:34.81,0:14:38.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a world that exists above our real world.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:39.35,0:14:42.97,Default,,0,0,0,,In an endless night, time does not move.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:42.97,0:14:48.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinpei and Ushio, can ya see that?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:48.69,0:14:49.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:49.99,0:14:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Now look at Ryuunosuke with those eyes.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:53.72,0:14:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryuu ain't ahead of us!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:56.43,0:14:57.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Yer right.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:57.39,0:14:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been talking without lapse.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:59.90,0:15:01.74,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why Shide wanted to bring us here.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:01.74,0:15:06.34,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't loop nor see two seconds ahead.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:06.72,0:15:10.47,Default,,0,0,0,,He's trying to steal Ushio's eye here.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:10.47,0:15:16.78,Default,,0,0,0,,The one with the awakened eye sees beyond the current world to a higher dimension.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:16.78,0:15:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,,He will have control of all of life, time, and space.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:22.60,0:15:29.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like how a three-dimensional person can easily pick up a comic book, throw it on the ground, and burn it.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:29.63,0:15:30.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:30.45,0:15:33.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously? It doesn't feel like I can do that!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:33.54,0:15:36.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It just awakened, so it seems unstable.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:36.85,0:15:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yer in an endless night too.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:39.63,0:15:43.98,Default,,0,0,0,,That eye is at its best in the real world.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:43.98,0:15:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,The ending...
Dialogue: 5,0:15:46.58,0:15:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the thought that I saw when I scanned Shide.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:51.76,0:15:53.97,Default,,0,0,0,,He wants to destroy the world,
Dialogue: 5,0:15:54.60,0:15:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,as if he's turning off a console.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:58.97,0:16:00.52,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing after that.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:01.63,0:16:03.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It's really the end.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:14.48,0:16:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I know this sound.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:19.92,0:16:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}An update from the central military district.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:22.55,0:16:27.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}B29s are headed north from Kii Channel.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:27.97,0:16:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}There are 250 enemy bombers\N headed north in five squadrons.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:34.56,0:16:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}One has circled over Awaji Island and is headed southeast.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:40.10,0:16:44.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}To all the citizens of Wakayama: we pray for your safety.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:44.11,0:16:46.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the air raid siren!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:01.71,0:17:03.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Ushio!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:03.01,0:17:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay down, Ryuu!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:04.77,0:17:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Ushio, don't make a shadow on the ground.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:07.35,0:17:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,The fire is dangerous.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:08.42,0:17:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep yer true form as small as possible!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:11.13,0:17:11.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm okay!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:11.97,0:17:13.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Shadows can't die here.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:13.79,0:17:15.35,Default,,0,0,0,,This doesn't hurt one bit.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:19.58,0:17:20.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Shide!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:21.10,0:17:26.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing can touch me, no matter what ya do.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:26.73,0:17:28.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Y'all look like slugs down there.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:29.32,0:17:36.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Ushio, first let me burn ya to a crisp, then I'll take yer eye.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:37.48,0:17:39.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So about what ya were saying...
Dialogue: 5,0:17:40.91,0:17:45.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Shide wants to use yer eye in the real world, right?
Dialogue: 5,0:17:45.54,0:17:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Which means there must be some way back to it!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:48.87,0:17:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinpei, yer right!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:50.70,0:17:52.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Kill Hiruko.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:52.67,0:17:55.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Even in an endless night,\N ya have the power to do that, Ushio.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:56.06,0:17:58.56,Default,,0,0,0,,The endless night disappears with Hiruko.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:58.56,0:18:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,We can go back to the real world.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:00.54,0:18:01.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Ya got it!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:02.44,0:18:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,But how?
Dialogue: 5,0:18:03.78,0:18:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Shide is way up in the sky.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:05.95,0:18:07.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave that to me.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:08.16,0:18:12.07,Default,,0,0,0,,This air raid is Hiruko's memory.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:09.17,0:18:10.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Stop...
Dialogue: 5,0:18:12.07,0:18:13.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It's hot...
Dialogue: 5,0:18:13.34,0:18:17.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm burning...
Dialogue: 5,0:18:17.06,0:18:24.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't make me relive... something like this...
Dialogue: 5,0:18:24.99,0:18:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a memory?
Dialogue: 5,0:18:26.11,0:18:29.13,Default,,0,0,0,,The endless night is linked to Hiruko's memory,
Dialogue: 5,0:18:29.48,0:18:33.59,Default,,0,0,0,,although I doubt this is a past she wants to remember.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:33.98,0:18:35.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Calm down.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:35.66,0:18:38.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if it hurts, it won't kill ya.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:38.67,0:18:43.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Yer pain gives 'em pain.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:46.56,0:18:48.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Shide forcing Hiruko to relive this!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:48.94,0:18:51.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Ushio, jump at my signal.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:51.49,0:18:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 5,0:18:52.00,0:18:54.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I have this memory too.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:54.71,0:18:58.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I can push it back fer a little while.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:58.94,0:19:01.12,Default,,0,0,0,,But beware of Shide's armor.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:01.69,0:19:08.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It works like an echo and sends an attack right back.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:09.56,0:19:13.07,Default,,0,0,0,,To defeat Shide, hack him, and erase the armor first.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:13.07,0:19:14.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Then we kill the inside.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:14.85,0:19:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a two-step process.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:16.24,0:19:19.49,Default,,0,0,0,,But after the first step, he'll get to Ushio.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:19.49,0:19:22.02,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I won't die.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:22.46,0:19:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Mio gave me something.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:25.27,0:19:26.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll finish him off in two steps, no matter what.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:27.58,0:19:31.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Before my hair burns away completely!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:31.05,0:19:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:32.19,0:19:35.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I can buy ya a few seconds.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:41.49,0:19:44.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Do ya trust me?
Dialogue: 5,0:19:44.46,0:19:45.49,Default,,0,0,0,,We do.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:46.47,0:19:49.67,Default,,0,0,0,,If my sister befriended ya, yer my friend too.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:50.38,0:19:52.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryuunosuke.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:52.55,0:19:54.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, Shinpei?
Dialogue: 5,0:19:54.68,0:19:55.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:56.71,0:19:57.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:01.80,0:20:03.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm ready.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:04.31,0:20:05.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:18.76,0:20:19.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Now!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:27.61,0:20:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I see you've got Haine on yer side.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:33.67,0:20:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm counting on ya, Ushio.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:36.30,0:20:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Stop Shide.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:39.57,0:20:44.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Let Hiruko rest in peace!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:48.64,0:20:50.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave it to me!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:50.73,0:20:53.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}At this height, I can't get to Ushio's true form.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:56.81,0:20:58.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They're fast and massive!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:58.16,0:21:00.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't avoid 'em with my hair.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:07.32,0:21:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll kill ya even in if I die too!
Dialogue: 5,0:21:16.72,0:21:17.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What?
Dialogue: 5,0:21:18.76,0:21:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What is he?
Dialogue: 5,0:21:20.27,0:21:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if ya die?
Dialogue: 5,0:21:23.11,0:21:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There's nothing inside!
Dialogue: 5,0:21:28.56,0:21:32.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That means I can't even try to trade blows.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:32.30,0:21:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,So ya read my mind.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:37.01,0:21:37.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He hacked—
Dialogue: 5,0:21:51.69,0:21:53.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She revived herself?
Dialogue: 5,0:21:53.22,0:21:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Did she eat a part of the original Ushio?
Dialogue: 5,0:21:58.11,0:21:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Then take this!
Dialogue: 5,0:22:10.04,0:22:11.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What did she do?!
Dialogue: 5,0:22:15.08,0:22:16.69,Default,,0,0,0,,The air raid stopped.
Dialogue: 5,0:22:17.11,0:22:19.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What happened?
Dialogue: 5,0:22:19.45,0:22:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She touched me to erase the memory of the air raid.
Dialogue: 5,0:22:23.79,0:22:25.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Shinpei, can ya hear me?
Dialogue: 5,0:22:25.25,0:22:25.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ushio!
Dialogue: 5,0:22:26.48,0:22:27.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I get it now.
Dialogue: 5,0:22:27.57,0:22:29.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Shide's body is in the real world.
Dialogue: 5,0:22:30.07,0:22:31.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}In the real world?!
Dialogue: 5,0:22:31.58,0:22:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Shide is remotely controlling his armor using Hiruko.
Dialogue: 5,0:22:36.53,0:22:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If there's nothing inside, there's not much we can do.
Dialogue: 5,0:22:40.83,0:22:43.09,Default,,0,0,0,,What does Shide's armor look like now?
Dialogue: 5,0:22:44.54,0:22:47.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The left half I erased is still gone.
Dialogue: 5,0:22:47.01,0:22:50.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Then erase the rest and go fer the win.
Dialogue: 5,0:22:51.52,0:22:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ushio?
Dialogue: 5,0:22:52.92,0:22:53.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ushio!
Dialogue: 5,0:22:54.94,0:22:54.94,Default,chapter,0,0,0,,{ED}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.92,0:23:01.58,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(200,200)}All traces of you vanished into the sea breeze
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.58,0:23:06.58,ED,,0,0,0,,{\c&H6173A3&\3c&H22C3F8&\blur5\fad(200,200)}But even now I still see visions of you
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.66,0:23:14.36,ED,,0,0,0,,{\c&HC3A644&\3c&HE9EBBB&\blur5\fad(200,200)}In reality I only have vivid memories
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.36,0:23:15.79,ED,,0,0,0,,{\c&HC3A644&\3c&HE9EBBB&\blur5\fad(200,0)}To play in my head over and over again
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.79,0:23:19.29,ED,,0,0,0,,{\3c&H9AFAF8&\blur5\fad(0,200)}To play in my head over and over again
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.59,0:23:24.69,ED,,0,0,0,,{\c&H6989A1&\3c&H73E97B&\blur5\fad(200,200)}Even if it's all just a lie
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.69,0:23:28.80,ED,,0,0,0,,{\c&H6989A1&\3c&H73E97B&\blur5\fad(200,200)}Please be close by my side
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.11,0:23:31.87,ED,,0,0,0,,{\c&H6A70EE&\3c&H83EF82&\blur5\fad(200,200)}Right next to me
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.27,0:23:37.62,ED,,0,0,0,,{\c&HE5D78D&\3c&HE4F4FB&\blur5\fad(200,200)}I fell for you before too long
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.62,0:23:40.69,ED,,0,0,0,,{\c&HE5D78D&\3c&HE4F4FB&\blur5\fad(200,0)}But time alone was what progressed
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.69,0:23:41.48,ED,,0,0,0,,{\c&H59A599&\3c&HF8EAC3&\blur5\fad(0,200)}But time alone was what progressed
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.99,0:23:45.97,ED,,0,0,0,,{\c&H59A599&\3c&HF8EAC3&\blur5\fad(0,200)}I wanna go back
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.27,0:23:54.96,ED,,0,0,0,,{\c&HB67647&\3c&HD0C1AC&\blur5\fad(200,200)}I've listened to my share of heartbreak songs
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.75,0:24:02.76,ED,,0,0,0,,{\c&HB67647&\3c&HD0C1AC&\blur5\fad(200,200)}Spending my days torn up and crying but now
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.76,0:24:05.31,ED,,0,0,0,,{\c&HB67647&\3c&HD0C1AC&\blur5\fad(200,200)}I want to move on
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.91,0:24:08.64,ED,,0,0,0,,{\c&HB67647&\3c&HD0C1AC&\blur5\fad(200,0)}I shouldn't act tough and just finally be
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.64,0:24:10.28,ED,,0,0,0,,{\c&HEBCEAB&\3c&HF4F3E8&\blur5\fad(0,200)}I shouldn't act tough and just finally be
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.56,0:24:13.56,ED,,0,0,0,,{\c&HEBCEAB&\3c&HF4F3E8&\blur5\fad(0,200)}True to myself
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.69,0:24:16.98,ED,,0,0,0,,{\c&HC16C32&\3c&HBFC385&\blur5\fad(200,0)}But it's too late for that
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.98,0:24:19.60,ED,,0,0,0,,{\c&HB4D1F0&\3c&HEAEEFD&\blur5\fad(0,200)}But it's too late for that
